summary:
Spider-Man: Far From Home speculation that I’m putting under a cut just to have it on record if I’m right.
They frame it in the...
body:
Spider-Man: Far From Home speculation that I’m putting under a cut just to have it on record if I’m right.

They frame it in the trailer that he left the suit behind because he just wanted to have a normal vacation, but May packed it anyway.

I don’t think that’s the case.

I think Endgame ends with him just being done being Spider-Man, perhaps because Tony dies, and May packs it because it almost to nudge him back into it.

I think those scenes with him high fiving May and showing up to get the check from Happy could quite possibly be from the end of Far From Home, and not the beginning.

The suit at that point is the Homecoming suit, but keep in mind they also gave Thor back his eye in the Ragnarok and Infinity War trailers.

They could alter that color scheme for a trailer.

…Also, with the scene of Fury showing up in his hotel room? I can see them adapting the scene from the Ultimate Venom arc where Peter wants to just be done, and Nick tells him that he needs to keep going and that he’s going to be one of the greats.
